---
layout: base.njk
title: "Writ Large — Federal Post-Conviction Articles"
description: "Plain-English guides to federal post-conviction relief, FSA time credits, compassionate release, and the procedural traps that sink good motions."
permalink: /blog/
---
<div class="page-head">
  <div class="wrap">
    <p class="eyebrow">Writ Large</p>
    <h1>Know the law they hope you never read.</h1>
  </div>
</div>
<section class="all-posts">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="posts">
      {% for post in collections.posts %}
      <a class="post" href="{{ post.url }}">
        <span class="kicker">{{ post.data.category }} · {{ post.date | dateDisplay }}</span>
        <h3>{{ post.data.title }}</h3>
        <p>{{ post.data.description }}</p>
        <span class="more">Read the post &rarr;</span>
      </a>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
